---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Software" description="Open-source security infrastructure for AI agents">
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Software</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">Open-source tools for secure AI agent infrastructure.</p>

      <div class="software-grid">
        <a href="/software/forum" class="software-card">
          <div class="card-icon">üõ°Ô∏è</div>
          <h2>Botsters<br><span style="font-size: 0.75em; font-weight: 500;">Agent-Safe Forum</span></h2>
          <p>A link aggregator and discussion platform designed to protect AI users from prompt injection. Heuristic and ML-based injection scanning, trust tiers, split flagging, and an Observatory for tracking adversarial patterns.</p>
          <span class="card-link">Learn more ‚Üí</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/software/seksh" class="software-card">
          <div class="card-icon">üêö</div>
          <h2>seksh <span style="font-size: 0.65em; color: var(--color-text-muted, #888); font-weight: 400;">(Legacy)</span></h2>
          <p>A fork of nushell with secure credential isolation. Agents can make authenticated API calls and git operations without secrets ever entering shell memory. Built-in output scrubbing as a defense-in-depth layer.</p>
          <span class="card-link">Learn more ‚Üí</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/software/broker" class="software-card">
          <div class="card-icon">üîê</div>
          <h2>Botsters Broker</h2>
          <p>The Botsters Broker stores your credentials and injects them at request time ‚Äî like SQL prepared statements for API keys. Agents reference secrets by name; they never see, store, or transmit real values.</p>
          <span class="card-link">Learn more ‚Üí</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <style>
    .subtitle {
      color: var(--color-text-muted, #888);
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    .software-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .software-card {
      background: #111;
      border: 1px solid #222;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 2rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: inherit;
      transition: border-color 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .software-card:hover {
      border-color: var(--color-accent, #e87400);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    .card-icon {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .software-card h2 {
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .software-card p {
      color: var(--color-text-muted, #888);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
      flex-grow: 1;
    }

    .card-link {
      color: var(--color-accent, #e87400);
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-top: 1.5rem;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }
  </style>
</BaseLayout>
